{
  "texts": [
    "Given x ′ ⊑ {x ∈ S ⊥ | R i ⊥ (x) ⊆ ↓y}, there is an x ∈ {x ∈ S ⊥ | R i ⊥ (x) ⊆ ↓y} such that x ′ ∧ x ̸ = ⊥ (cf.",
    "Fact 5.12), so x ′ ∧ x ⊑ x ′.",
    "Let x ′′ = x ′ ∧ x.",
    "Then by (i), there is a z ′′ ≬ z ′ such that x ′′ R i z ′′.",
    "Given x ′′ R i z ′′ ≬ z ′ and x ′′ ⊑ x, it follows by R-rule that there is a u such that xR i u ≬ z ′."
  ]
}